      {
        "title": "Say Hello to PICK!",
        "description": "A brand-new concept camera, the PowerShot PICK is your smart personal photographer at your back and call. Just say a simple voice command and it will compose, shoot and recommend the best shot for you. Just sit back, relax, and let PowerShot PICK do the job for you!"
